Google+ API

In this tutorial you will learn how to:

     1) Design login page using Bootstrap Design
     2) add "Login With Google" button to the login page
     3)  create Client ID and Client Secret Code
     4) get permission for Google Account
     5) generate Google OAuth 2.0 Code
     6) generate Access Token
     7) display Google Account Data inside your website

