Errors : 


Possiblity of error comes : 
	

	Error Will be like Fatal error: Uncaught exception 'cURL_Exception' with message 'cURL resource: Resource id #10; cURL error: SSL certificate problem: unable to get local issuer certificate (cURL error code 60). See http://curl.haxx.se/libcurl/c/libcurl... for an explanation of error codes.' in Here is the Link of root certificate bundle: https://curl.haxx.se/ca/cacert.pem Copy this certificate bundle on your disk. And use this on php.ini curl.cainfo = "path_to_cert\cacert.pem" 
	
	
